<template>

</template>

<script>
import ProductDataService from '@/services/ProductDataService.js'
export default {
  data () {
    return {
      products: []
    }
  },
  mounted () {
    ProductDataService.getAll()
      .then(response => {
        this.products = response.data
      })
  }
}
</script>
